file.name: additional-properties.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Skip additional properties
  version: '1.0'
servers:
  - url: 'http://localhost:3000'
paths:
  /v1/roles:
    get:
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
components:
  schemas:
    User:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
    Implicit:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
    ExplicitSkip:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
      additionalProperties: false
    ExplicitKeep:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
      additionalProperties: true
